_sText: SURF_JAPAN_RELOADED Map done by Rebell in 2007-2008! ABOUT: ------ This map is a complete rebuild version of the original one from MonkeyDie. This reloaded map is in dust style and has the maximum at FPS-optimisation. I hope it works good on your PC. INFOS: ------ This map has now only 14mb filesize. Ive added a new jail where you can play a knife-soccergame to escape. There are 3 healthpacks to get full health. And there is also a secret with a special weapon! CREDITS: -------- MONKEYDIE - for the original map (thanks man this was the first surfmap ive ever played and learned howto surf *gg*) KRUSTY - for testing, bugreporting and additional help! ALL PLAYERS AT MY SERVER! ... a video will come properly soon - cya Rebell ;-)
